column4: NSLOCTEXT("[BEEBD2B843335B98999FC88AED8C42CA]", "65AEA7354A43D0F3E987DBA3D9BDFD7F", "I don\'t know if it helps, but here are some fishing tips.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BEEBD2B843335B98999FC88AED8C42CA]", "F25BF0484BCC0F0FA579A6BEE11C9240", "First, a fishing rod. A good one can fly far and has enough flex.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BEEBD2B843335B98999FC88AED8C42CA]", "FB4705854293233B30351DB95009B7E8", "Next, bait. Remember which fish you caught with which bait.")
NSLOCTEXT("[BEEBD2B843335B98999FC88AED8C42CA]", "AEE8BA5B4A5F5CA1F949F799E4254A16", "When you throw the rod, release with [E] to let it fly at full power!")
NSLOCTEXT("[BEEBD2B843335B98999FC88AED8C42CA]", "F5B866E746D0FE73A63260A9E5043CCC", "About the Lake Guardian... He appears in the morning and late afternoon everyday.")
